## üß† Core Idea  
A **virtual monitoring center** staffed by **virtual software agents**, each assigned to monitor a specific person, place, thing, system, or process. These agents operate at **virtual workstations**, use **specialized software**, and participate in an **organizational hierarchy** that enables reporting, oversight, and continuous improvement.

This creates a digital ecosystem where every monitored entity receives focused, intelligent attention.

