## üß© 4. Organizational Hierarchy  
Your concept includes a **chain of oversight**, where:

- Agents report upward to supervisory agents or human managers  
- Supervisors can observe agent performance  
- Insights flow upward and downward  
- Knowledge is shared across the organization  

This creates a **learning organization** where improvements propagate system‚Äëwide.

